Package com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.collection

Interface Sectionable<Value,Section extends Addable<Value> & Indexable<Value>>

Type Parameters:
Value - The value being indexed
Section - A type that can contain subsections of an Indexable, normally a list
All Superinterfaces:
Addable<Value>, Emptiness, Factory<Section>, Indexable<Value>, Iterable<Value>, Joinable<Value>, Sequence<Value>, Sized, SpaceLimited
public interface Sectionable<Value,Section extends Addable<Value> & Indexable<Value>> extends Indexable<Value>, Addable<Value>, Factory<Section>
Retrieves different subsections from an Indexable.
